    %body.init


        %section#question{:'data-0'=>'transform:translate3d(0,0%, 0);', :'data-top-bottom'=>'transform:translate3d(0, 15%, 0);'}
            .bounds
                %p.lead Which do we address first?
                %h1
                    %span.animate-block-1
                        poverty
                    %em.animate-block-2
                        or
                    %span.animate-block-3
                        education

                .scroll-prompt
                    %small scroll down to learn more
                    .icon{:'data-icon'=>'a'}

            .content-background

        %section#philosophy
            .bounds
                %h1.fadeOn-one
                    We believe longterm solutions
                    %br/
                    will address both

                %p.lead.fadeOn-two EdBuild was created to rethink schools and rebuild communities.

                %p
                    We explore the intersection of education reform and economic development,
                    and we provide tangible solutions that support the revitalization of states,
                    cities, and school districts.

                %p.fadeOn-three
                    %strong
                        We are EdBuild. Let's rebuild the future.



        %section#problem
            .bounds
                %h2.fadeOn-one
                    When neighborhoods suffer,
                    %br/
                    schools fail.


                %h2.fadeOn-two
                    And when schools fail,
                    %br/
                    neighborhoods suffer.

            .content-background{:'data-500'=>'transform:translate3d(0, 0px, 0);', :'data-top-bottom'=>'transform:translate3d(0, -200px, 0);'}


        %section#approach-1
            .bounds
                %p.center
                    %strong
                        To address this cycle, our work focuses on three key areas where economic development and education reform intersect.

                .content-row.col-ten.col-center
                    .card
                        .icon-gear{:'data-icon'=>'g'}
                        %h4.title Infrastructure
                        %p
                            We believe that rightsizing building portfolios and providing charter schools with development incentives can bring more resources to districts and communities while increasing quality school options for families.

                    .card
                        .icon-gear{:'data-icon'=>'g'}
                        %h4.title Workforce
                        %p
                            We believe that smart compensation and pension systems will attract and retain the best teachers to inspire students in struggling schools and contribute to the local economy by living in the neighborhoods in which they teach.


                    .card
                        .icon-gear{:'data-icon'=>'g'}
                        %h4.title Resources
                        %p
                            We believe that adequate funding and efficient spending can spur innovation and ensure
                            %em
                                every
                            public school student has the resources they need to succeed.




        %section#approach-2
            .bounds
                %p
                    %strong
                        Our three-tiered approach will help leaders at every level, from district superintendents to governors.



        %section#approach-3

            %ul.highlights-list
                %li.highlight-one
                    .icon-container.col-one
                        .icon{:'data-icon'=>'h'}
                    .copy-container.col-eight
                        %h1 Drive New Thinking
                        %p
                            Through the compilation of data, the encouragement of discourse and debate, and the development of innovative new communications strategies.

                %li.highlight-two
                    .icon-container.col-one
                        .icon{:'data-icon'=>'e'}
                    .copy-container.col-eight
                        %h1 Reveal Pathways for Change
                        %p
                            By tracking emerging research, and partnering with respected peers to support the pursuit of evidence in these areas.
                %li.highlight-three
                    .icon-container.col-one
                        .icon{:'data-icon'=>'f'}
                    .copy-container.col-eight
                        %h1 Implement Innovation
                        %p
                            By building actionable data-based models, and guiding stakeholders through the implementation of new and innovative strategies â€“ every step of the way.

        %section#contact{:role => "contentinfo"}
            .bounds
                %p.lead.fadeUp-one
                    %strong
                        It's time to Rebuild the Promise of The American Dream.

                %h1.fadeUp-two
                    It's time to rethink schools &amp; rebuild our communities.
                .logo-wrap.fadeOn-three
                    %img{:src => "../img/logos/logo+@2x.png", :alt => "edbuild"}/


                %p
                    Drop us a line sometime at
                    %a{:href => "mailto:contact@edbuild.org"}
